      "query": "What categories of products does igus.de offer? List the main product families with one example each.",
      "agent": {
        "text": "igus specializes in \"Motion Plastics,\" offering components designed for continuous movement without the need for external lubrication. The main product families available on igus.de include:\n\n1. **Energy Chains (e-chain®)**: Polymer cable and hose carrier systems designed to guide and protect moving cables in machinery.\n*Example SKU:* `E4.32.10.150.0` (E4.32 series standard snap-open cable chain).\n\n2. **Flexible Cables (chainflex®)**: Control, motor, data, and servo cables engineered specifically to withstand millions of bending cycles inside moving energy chains.\n*Example SKU:* `CF5.05.18` (chainflex® CF5 PVC unscreened 18-core control cable).\n\n3. **Polymer Bearings (iglidur®)**: Self-lubricating, maintenance-free plain, flanged, and sleeve bearings. \n*Example SKU:* `ASM-0103-02` (iglidur® A200 FDA-compliant sleeve bearing).\n\n4. **Linear Technology (drylin®)**: Linear guides, slide tables, and actuators that run completely dry on polymer sliding elements rather than recirculating ball bearings.\n*Example SKU:* `WS-10-40` (drylin® W hard-anodized aluminum round single rail).\n\nAdditionally, igus offers related product lines like **igubal®** (spherical/rod end bearings) and **Low-Cost Automation** (robotics, multi-axis gantries, and gearboxes).",
